Interface Nlp.OnInitializationListener

  • Enclosing class:
    Nlp

    public static interface Nlp.OnInitializationListener
    Represents a listener to provide notification of the Nlp status upon completion of initialization.
    See Also:
    Nlp.init(Context, MapFragment, CollectionProvider, SpeechToTextProvider, Nlp.OnInitializationListener), Nlp.init(Context, Map, MapGesture, CollectionProvider, SpeechToTextProvider, Nlp.OnInitializationListener)

      • onComplete

        void onComplete(Error error)
        A callback indicating that that Nlp initialization has completed.
        Parameters:
        error - If Nlp initialized successfully, returns Error.NONE. Otherwise, Error.FAILED with a message indicating the reason of initialization failure.
